msgstr "選擇您的主題"

#: front-page.php:305
msgid "Pick the topics you care about and we'll show you the meetings that matter."
msgstr "選擇您關心的主題，我們將為您顯示相關的重要會議。"

#: front-page.php:320
msgid "Civic tools"
msgstr "公民工具"

#: front-page.php:322
